 Controversial Nigerian Actress Tonto Dikeh has got her fans on social media talking following an unusual and revealing stunt. Sharing the video on her page, the movie star and her son, King Andre, were spotted in the company of an unknown man and other kids at a recreational centre. In the clip, Tonto put up a weird somersault while revealing a part of the body which seemingly ought not to be exposed. WATCH VIDEO BELOW Shortly after sharing the video, the comment section was flooded with mixed reactions from fans and followers of the actress. Some of them claimed they saw something while watching her doing the weird somersault. SEE REACTIONS BELOW  